  "decision_conditions": [
    "Reason : 1 - REASON: The proposed roof terrace by reason of its inappropriate design, location, prominent siting, and height would form a dominant and discordant addition to the host property and wider terrace setting. The addition would be readily visible from the surrounding private realm and would cause clear visual harm and would therefore be contrary to policies D4 of the London Plan (2021), policies CS8 and CS9 of the Islington Core Strategy 2011, policy DM2.1 of the Islington Development Management Policy 2013 and the Islington Urban Design Guide 2017.",
    "Reason : 2 - REASON: The inappropriate siting of the proposed amenity terrace and insufficient separation distance would have a material adverse impact on the rear habitable windows of amenity of neighbouring properties along Stonenest Street, immediately adjacent to the application site, in terms of loss of overlooking and privacy, contrary to Policy DM2.1 of the Islington Development Management Policies 2013."
